Description.description: Captures the details of an individual component of a Project Budget.

The award-related cost category that is associated with this budget line.

Specified by the budget author. The amount this budget line is expected to contribute to the overall budget amount.

Refers to how much of the referenced Workers time and therefore cost is expected to be associated with this plan. A percentage expressed as a decimal (i.e. 100% = 1.000).
Refers to the GL Account the amount should be tracked against.

Refers to the Project Budget this budget line belongs to.
